text: Frederick Leslie Estabrooks (October 16, 1876 – January 31, 1974) was a Canadian politician. He served in the Legislative Assembly of New Brunswick as member of the Liberal party representing Westmorland County from 1921 to 1925. ==References== Category:20th-century Canadian politicians Category:1876 births Category:1974 deaths Category:New Brunswick Liberal Association MLAs
title: Frederick L. Estabrooks
